data.description:
Welcome to 502 Kevin Road, a charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood. This property is brimming with features that are sure to impress!
As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the open concept layout, creating a sense of spaciousness and allowing for seamless flow between the living areas. The kitchen boasts wooden countertops, a gas range, dishwasher, and microwave – perfect for whipping up delicious meals for family and friends.
The home is equipped with modern conveniences, including a new AC system installed in 2018, high impact certified metal roof, security system, and security cameras for added peace of mind. Stay connected with WiFi smoke detectors that provide an extra layer of safety.
Outside, you'll find a new concrete drive leading to the one-car garage and an expansive backyard that exudes a country feel. The .57-acre lot offers ample space and privacy to enjoy outdoor activities or indulge your green thumb. Plus, it's chicken friendly!
For those seeking additional storage or workshop space, the oversized shop with electric and AC window unit will surely impress. And don't forget about the oversized storm cellar – providing protection during inclement weather.
Located just an hour from Tulsa and 50 minutes from OKC, this property offers a convenient location with easy access to city amenities while still enjoying the tranquility of a suburban setting. Commuting to Shawnee is a breeze at just 25 minutes away.
Motivated sellers are offering a VA assumable loan at a competitive rate of 2.75% for qualified applicants. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your dream home! Call today to schedule your private showing.
